 The registered version includes:
 - lots of new Levels
 - a Preferences program to configure Diamond Caves
 - a nice Leveleditor
 - two programs to include your own graphics
   and your own samples into Diamond Caves!
 - a 32 color-version of the game

 This disk may be freely distributed as long as all files
